title: Film Theory: Jurassic World Was An INSIDE JOB! (Jurassic World) Views:3,869,621 Posted:6 months ago
content: About   SUBSCRIBE for More Film Theories! ► http://bit.ly/1dI8VBH  Don’t Fly to Mordor!! ►► https://goo.gl/bQvgSs  Rey’s Parents SOLVED! (Star Wars) ►► https://goo.gl/g1wBYm   JURASSIC WORLD follows the same outline as the previous Jurassic movies – humans decide recreating dinosaurs would be fun, something goes wrong with the system designed to imprison them, and a cool amusement park turns into a horrific monster-filled island. But what if it wasn’t so simple? What if the dinosaur fiasco in Jurassic World wasn’t an accident? Strap in, Loyal Theorists. In this episode, I will prove that the dinosaurs didn’t escape from Jurassic World. They were set free!
